sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Intel Corp ( INTC ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 3.2%.
Year to date, Intel Corp has lost about 0.9% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Home Depot ( HD ), trading down 2.2%.
Home Depot is lower by about 7.6% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Cisco Systems ( CSCO ), trading down 2.2%, and Procter & Gamble Company ( PG ), trading down 0.0% on the day.
